ropean Union NextGenerationEU (PRTR-C17.I1) and by Generalitat de Catalunya (In-CAEM Project). ICN2 is supported by the Severo Ochoa program from the Spanish MCIN / AEI (Grant No.: CEX2021-001214-S) and is funded by the CERCA Programme / Generalitat de Catalunya. Part of the present work has been performed in the framework of the Universitat Autònoma de Barcelona Materials Science PhD program. ICN2 acknowledges funding from Grant IU16-014206 (METCAM-FIB) funded by the European Union through the European Regional Development Fund (ERDF), with the support of the Ministry of Research and Universities, Generalitat de Catalunya. ICN2 is a founding member of e-DREAM<sup><a data-track="click" data-track-action="reference anchor" data-track-label="link" data-test="citation-ref" aria-label="Reference 217" title="Ciancio, R. et al. e-DREAM: the European Distributed Research Infrastructure for Advanced Electron Microscopy. Microsc. Microanal. 28, 2900–2902 (2022)." href="/articles/s43246-026-01133-w#ref-CR217" id="ref-link-section-d281700530e3400">217</a></sup>. Co-funded by the European Union. Views and opinions expressed are, however, those of the author(s) only and do not necessarily reflect those of the European Union or the European Research Executive Agency. Neither the European Union nor the granting authority can be held responsible for them.</p></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby="author-information" data-title="Author information"><div class="c-article-section" id="author-information-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="author-information">Author information</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="author-information-content"><span class="c-article-author-information__subtitle u-visually-hidden" id="author-notes">Author notes</span><ol class="c-article-author-information__list"><li class="c-article-author-information__item" id="na1"><p>These authors contributed equally: Alessandra Manzini, Irina Martynova.</p></li></ol><h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="affiliations">Authors and Affiliations</h3><ol class="c-article-author-affiliation__list"><li id="Aff1"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">CY University, Cergy, France</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Alessandra Manzini</p></li><li id="Aff2"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Catalonia Institute for Energy Research (IREC), Sant Adrià de Besòs, Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Irina Martynova,&nbsp;Jing Yu,&nbsp;Xiaoyu Bi,&nbsp;Jordi Jacas Biendicho,&nbsp;Qing Sun&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Andreu Cabot</p></li><li id="Aff3"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Catalan Institute of Nanoscience and Nanotechnology (ICN2), CSIC and BIST, Campus UAB, Bellaterra, Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Jing Yu&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Jordi Arbiol</p></li><li id="Aff4"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">ICREA Pg. Lluis Companys, Barcelona, Spain</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Jordi Arbiol&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Andreu Cabot</p></li><li id="Aff5"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">College of Materials Science and Engineering, Fuzhou University, Fuzhou City, Fujian Province, China</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Chaoqi Zhang</p></li></ol><div class="u-js-hide u-hide-print" data-test="author-info"><span class="c-article__sub-heading">Authors</span><ol class="c-article-authors-search u-list-reset"><li id="auth-Alessandra-Manzini-Aff1"><span class="c-article-authors-search__title u-h3 js-search-name">Alessandra Manzini</span><div class="c-article-authors-search__list"><div class="c-article-authors-search__item c-article-authors-search__list-item--left"><a href="/search?author=Alessandra%20Manzini" class="c-article-button" data-track="click" data-track-action="author link - publication" data-tr